main event: A bright, silvery or golden object was observed in the sky with rapid motion, disappearing over the horizon in about 30 seconds.
interesting points: The sighting occurred on February 25, 1961, at 0235 in the morning., The observation lasted for 30 seconds., The object was noted to have no sound and left no trail., A request for additional information was sent but no further details were received., The project related to this sighting is part of the Project Blue Book investigation.
sighted object: bright silvery or golden object in the sky
